Package runner

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BenchmarkRunner
    This class contains a runner used to measure the runtime of the core frechet distance and Isomap implementations.
    ColorByElevation
    ColorByElevation is used to color GeographicPolygons by their elevation.
    ColorByLatitude
    ColorByLatitude is used to color GeographicPolygons by their latitude.
    ColorByLongitude
    ColorByLongitude is used to color GeographicPolygons by their longitude.
    CoverageMap
    A CoverageMap is used to generate a map-like image representation from a List of GeographicGridPolygon.
    GenerateCoverageMaps
    This class contains a runner used to generate complete coverage maps using three different coloring schemes.
    GridWeatherScatterPlotRunner
    This class contains a runner used to display the 3d embedding of Polygons generated from the grid weather dataset.
    ScatterPlot
    A ScatterPlot displaying a set of points in 3d space.
    ShiftedSpikeScatterPlotRunner
    This class contains a runner used to display the 3d embedding of the shifted spike dataset.
    WeatherPolygonPainter
    A WeatherPolygonPainter is used to color GeographicPolygons using a certain coloring scheme.
    WeatherScatterPlot
    A ScatterPlot displaying a set of points in 3d space.
    WeatherStationsScatterPlotRunner
    This class contains a runner used to display the 3d embedding of Polygons generated from the weather stations dataset.
